I"@<p>еңЁдёҠдёҖи®ІдёӯжҲ‘д»¬еӯҰд№ дәҶ while иҜӯеҸҘиҝӣиЎҢеҫӘзҺҜжҺ§еҲ¶пјҢжҺҘдёӢжқҘжҲ‘д»¬е°ҶиҰҒеӯҰд№ еҸҰдёҖз§ҚеҫӘзҺҜиҜӯеҸҘ for гҖӮ</p>

<h2 class="tut-h2-pad" id="еҹәжң¬дҪҝз”Ё">еҹәжң¬дҪҝз”Ё
  <a href="/tutorials/python-basic/basic/03-2-for/#еҹәжң¬дҪҝз”Ё" class="headerlink" title="Permalink to this headline">В¶</a>
</h2>

<p>дёҚеҗҢзј–зЁӢиҜӯиЁҖйғҪжңү for иҜӯиЁҖпјҢжҜ”еҰӮ C# иҜӯиЁҖдёӯзҡ„ <strong>foreach</strong>, Java иҜӯиЁҖдёӯзҡ„ <strong>for</strong>,еңЁ Python
дёӯзҡ„еҹәжң¬дҪҝз”Ёж–№жі•еҰӮдёӢгҖӮ</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">item</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">sequence</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="n">expressions</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">sequence</code> дёәеҸҜиҝӯд»Јзҡ„еҜ№иұЎпјҢ<code class="highlighter-rouge">item</code> дёәеәҸеҲ—дёӯзҡ„жҜҸдёӘеҜ№иұЎгҖӮ</p>

<h2 class="tut-h2-pad" id="е®һдҫӢ">е®һдҫӢ
  <a href="/tutorials/python-basic/basic/03-2-for/#е®һдҫӢ" class="headerlink" title="Permalink to this headline">В¶</a>
</h2>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">example_list</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">12</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">543</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">876</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">12</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">i</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">example_list</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">)</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>иҫ“еҮәзҡ„з»“жһңдёә <code class="highlighter-rouge">1,2,3,4,5,6,7,12,543,876,12,3,2,5</code>, еҶ…е®№дҫқж¬Ўдёә <code class="highlighter-rouge">example_list</code> дёӯзҡ„жҜҸдёҖдёӘе…ғзҙ 
жіЁж„Ҹ Python жҳҜдҪҝз”Ёзј©иҝӣиЎЁзӨәзЁӢеәҸзҡ„з»“жһ„пјҢеҰӮжһңзЁӢеәҸиҝҷж ·зј–еҶҷпјҢ</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">example_list</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">12</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">543</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">876</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">12</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">i</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">example_list</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'inner of for'</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'outer of for'</span><span class="p">)</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>йӮЈд№ҲжҜҸж¬ЎеҫӘзҺҜйғҪдјҡиҫ“еҮә <code class="highlighter-rouge">inner of for</code>,еңЁеҫӘзҺҜз»“жқҹеҗҺпјҢиҫ“еҮә <code class="highlighter-rouge">outer of for</code> дёҖж¬ЎгҖӮ</p>

